description:
Dataset of the captured small mammals and the codes used for the analysis in R for an investigation of the &quot;Prevalence of Pathogenic Leptospirosis spp in non-volant small mammals of Human Lipur Sekayu, Terengganu, Malaysia&quot;. 

 &nbsp; 

 The file &quot;small_mammals.csv&quot; represents the details of the captured small mammals, their species, gender, weight and the PCR result for both positive and negative samples.

